Name: You Only Livez Twice
About the game: It's after the zombie apocalypse and you want to survive at all costs. Do you have what it takes? Play as both humans and zombies in this 2d survival game. Each has a different strategy for winning. Play as Humans Start with nothing and quickly find weapons to protect yourself. Just don't let yourself get close to a zombie horde. Play as Zombies Build a giant horde and overwhelm your opponents through sheer force. Single player Develop your skills against the computer to prepare yourself for the multiplayer onslaught.
